text: So far many visits, Service staff Adeline service was great n attentive. She never fails to check if we have enough ice for our hard liquor or even if our drinks are finishing. She sings well and entertains her customers. I believe Adeline's attitude and friendliness brings in many customers to return back. Atmosphere cosy and clean.
Chill and very adequately done up. With a pool table in the middle.
The Atmosphere is perfect. The Food has a good choice & excellent. Service there is good. The staff is very patient with my orders
A cosy nice place to chill out with your friends!
